snippet.title: Neo Harbor Rescue Squad - Official Announcement Trailer (4K)
snippet.description:
Neo Harbor Rescue Squad lets you live the life of a rookie paramedic through frantic minigame action and a wild, funny story. Juggle waves of patients with a battle-like triage system; master dozens of treatment minigames; and win the city's recognition from the rival fire department in this paramedic action drama!

From the creators of Home, Alone With You, and Worse Than Death!

Wishlist today on Steam: https://go.bancy.co/NeoHarborSteam
Official website: https://www.jointherescuesquad.com/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/KECSNutNkm

#indiegame #PS5 #PS4 #steam
